005package edu.wpi.first.networktables;
006
007/**
008 * NetworkTables String entry.
009 *
010 * <p>Unlike NetworkTableEntry, the entry goes away when close() is called.
011 */
012public interface StringEntry extends StringSubscriber, StringPublisher {
013  /** Stops publishing the entry if it's published. */
014  void unpublish();
015}
